message.body: Hi what are your plans for the summer
Hey there. I'm going on vacation in a few weeks. Other than that, I'm just working and enjoying being off from school. What about you ?
Ooo vacation sounds great! I'm finishing up two summer classes rn but will prob be job hunting once theyre done
I was gonna take summer classes but they seem like a ton of work in such a short time
They are! It would be too much if I had actual things to do haha
Yeah I wanted to just enjoy my time off but I ended up being bored half the time. But I guess that's not the worst thing in the world
I def wanna go to the spa
Lol me too if spas weren't so expensive I'd be at one every day
